{"tid":1537661,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"有內地人參加香港遊行被拘留10日，眾叛親離、終日惶恐","createTime":"2019-09-04T04:06:45.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-04T04:37:04.000Z","uid":215634,"like":19,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":15,"replies":[{"pid":"4db6b5c56f82887092a07f540ebbf49d7e806606","tid":1537661,"uid":215634,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-04T04:06:45.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://i.imgur.com/TFoY0Mk.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi.imgur.com%2FTFoY0Mk.jpg&h=2a522f25&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n品葱論壇轉發，來源不明。<a href=\"https://pincong.rocks/article/4514\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fpincong.rocks%2Farticle%2F4514&d=8FXSm2SwW1drj%2BZzPONh3LM5QgR%2FpIHXQ%2BfAgFWVWJ0%3D&h=b7b0b6fe\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://pincong.rocks/article/4514</a><br />\n<br />\n喺香港我地最少都有二百萬同路人，但係事主身邊基本上所有人都反對佢，壓力一定比我地大好多。希望大家唔好放棄，我地抗爭成功之後，要令內地同路人呼吸自由的空氣。<br />\n<br />\n我地要繼續抗爭、絕不停止。"},{"pid":"768fc8caf228060891a0e2718183db42d015715d","tid":1537661,"uid":123991,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-04T04:06:53.000Z","msg":"<div style=\"text-align: center;\"><strong>9月7日 (六) 1PM<br />\n機場交通壓力測試 (重考)</strong></div><br />\n<br />\n香港市民：<br />\n✅ 以遊客身份入機場觀賞飛機升降 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n✅ 唔識路就坐多幾轉車 <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/cook.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n✅ 必需繳付車資乘坐黨鐵<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/wet.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/lick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n烏克蘭, 法國等其他國藉居民：<br />\n各有各做, 自由發揮, 唔割但要小心 <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/sowhat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n另外可參考唔揸春袋揸輸精管方法: <img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/wet.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/jable.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n [行動post] 肯入黎睇9.7點樣揸機場輸精管未 | LIHKG <br />\n <a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/1535579/page/1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/1535579/page/1</a> <br />\n <br />\n <br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/nyixFQQ.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FnyixFQQ.png&h=cc1f24a6&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\"><strong>9月8日 (日) 2PM<br />\n香港人權與民主法案集會<br />\n美國駐港澳總領事館</strong></div><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/2GKH20p.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F2GKH20p.png&h=6178433f&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"d17f011929b5f16c84da0ea92c948f893b83fa28","tid":1537661,"uid":55913,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-04T04:07:33.000Z","msg":"勇士<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"748ec697ac09378b52ce6d0e5bb290b6ce5c0208","tid":1537661,"uid":108347,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-04T04:08:32.000Z","msg":"求吓大家，暫停鑽牛角尖睇多啲評論<br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1537499\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1537499</a>"},{"pid":"4e9eabf1311cc605bd27abe604a9e69bfb915031","tid":1537661,"uid":134107,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-04T04:10:56.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/mqNCcpj.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FmqNCcpj.jpg&h=145b357e&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n[10月1送大禮]「和理拍」一齊推上聯合國人權理事會！！!<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1536307\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1536307</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"29d3b28e2e882d30aa0517b885c1f06bf9f02db7","tid":1537661,"uid":264121,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-04T04:14:20.000Z","msg":"慘"},{"pid":"25c515780a923ab1a36da302a3826534788a0729","tid":1537661,"uid":215634,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-04T04:17:34.000Z","msg":"推1/10"},{"pid":"e37045f5eb0